ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would absolutely recommend this seminar to any fellow student interested in contemporary Francophone Literature, the french class-system and critical theory.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This class exposed my to a myriad of texts and writers I would have never known of, let alone read, had I not participated in it, and I therefore feel incredibly enriched by it. My research will doubtlessly benefit from these new textual acquaintances and especially from the understanding that it is not only possible but crucial to research contemporary literature.
